% to check the cloning protocol (https or ssh)
git remote -v

% To switch from https to ssh:
git remote set-url origin git@github.com:ucsdbiodynamicslab/ucsdbiodynamicslab.github.io.git

%To clone project to a local computer:
git clone git@github.com:ucsdbiodynamicslab/ucsdbiodynamicslab.github.io.git

% To push to a "lev" branch:
git checkout -b lev

% To push project to github:
git add .  _or_ git add <path/filename>
git commit -m “adding lev pages”
git push
